{"title":"怒江小诗","authors":["晓雪"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":7,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"怒江小诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晓雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪杉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"根扎得很深很深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腰挺得很直很直，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经历了多少回沧桑变化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抗击过多少次雪暴风狂！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你从不后悔，毫不动摇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不怕寂寞，不畏奇寒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就选定这高海拔的岗位，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远与碧罗雪山作伴！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攀登"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有舒适，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有平坦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步步坎坷崎岖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处行路艰难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一步都需要攀登，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一步都需要流汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而每一次攀登，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都会获得新的惊喜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美的报偿；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一座山峰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都会给你诗的灵感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奇丽的风光！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是开不败的花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是摘不下的花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是会奔跑的花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是爱唱歌的花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从怒江上游到下游，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一百里、三百里、五百里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你一路盛开一路欢唱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当你汇入大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便与来自四面八方的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更多的花朵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高唱着碰撞着竞相开放！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":11,"page_end":11}